txt.en: You have defeated many Spiders in Western Osgiliath.

'Spiders from the East have marched into the city, most likely under command of the Morgul army. It seems they found a way to cross the river.\n\n'I'm sending you out there to kill any of those creatures you can find. I don't need those beasts ambushing my soldiers.'
Edenos has tasked you with defeating encroaching spiders from the Morgul Vale that have recently crossed the river.
You have defeated many Spiders thus making the Western side of the city a safer place to defend against the enemy.
Spiders can be found on the Western side of Osgiliath.\n\nYou should defeat the encroaching Spiders.
